{"tid":1840741,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] #AbC 家居儲糧 外國綠色蔬菜推介","createTime":"2020-01-25T03:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T14:03:45.000Z","uid":20454,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"adaff8a333774d03cd768d4cdcb55441dc5802ee","tid":1840741,"uid":20454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:36:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的，2016年開始我就開始戒中國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至會專注於屋企煮飯要除左水喉水之外都去中國化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以Anywhere but China黎講，個人覺得最困難就係綠色蔬菜<br />\n因為貴！<br />\n就例如呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日食真係唔掂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10cLc3c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10cLc3c.png&h=e91525c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新鮮菜Tldr:<br />\n最平應該係西芹，America<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各大超市<br />\n椰菜/旺菜/菇：日式超市買，日本<br />\n翠玉瓜：吉之島見過韓國，未食過<br />\n<br />\n我之前一段長時間都係吉之島輪流買日本椰菜同旺菜黎食<br />\n甚至會係吉之島冰櫃買一細包幾十蚊日式雜菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次要開post講係因為見到台灣friend有一日係facebook話自己係costco買左2kg急凍西蘭花<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來我以為香港得呢啲垃圾雜豆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxWW4hm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxWW4hm.png&h=bc28efc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但好快就搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vggDybb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvggDybb.png&h=9952d76f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPaptKw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPaptKw.png&h=d388f379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rhkdm5g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhkdm5g.png&h=99ea3486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n菠菜係分好哂一粒粒<br />\n每次倒兩三粒出黎叮到解凍，再撈入去我煮緊嘅野度<br />\n西蘭花我未開，但應該直接放牛油鹽叮都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> $29.9/1kg<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔洗食中國菜</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗洗菜切菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1kg係1kg都食得，無爛菜頭菜尾要丟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企少人都唔驚食唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：岩岩趁早買咗幾包all in冰格先開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家武漢肺炎個勢應該好快會炒貴啲中國菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名睇廢老捱貴菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4812af40ab716baa2aa76041a9decede462a8d15","tid":1840741,"uid":20454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:50:14.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c0d1e7a27d781e0114db42e4297fb975a564378d","tid":1840741,"uid":20454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1bab336b66860d15a5963d2feffb2917c067508c","tid":1840741,"uid":20454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"8"